  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "2. Add garlic and onion, sauté until softened.",
    "3. Add chicken, cook until browned on both sides.",
    "4. Add sherry, melange, and chicken broth, stir to combine.",
    "5. Bring mixture to a simmer, cook until reduced by half.",
    "6. Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
